\cf0 This module comes not only from the need to consolidate all bass drum sound parameters into a single module but most importantly, because it is a single module, there are no mismatches between triggers and envelopes, which can happen when building a modular bass drum sound, causing the sound to be inconsistent from one kick to another.\
\
